title: Trevor Lawrence's NFL Checklist
description:
Wendi Nix, Todd McShay and David Pollack discuss how COVID is affecting the status of SEC games and their defenses. They also talk about the power house that is Trevor Lawrence as well as Mississippi State and UNC.
